{
  "uid": "v12-1-advisor",
  "title": "Grafana 12.1 — Grafana Advisor",
  "description": "Enterprise-grade health & inventory dashboard for the v12.1 Grafana Advisor. KPIs (totals by category, signature, Angular), distribution charts, full plugin inventory with marketplace cross-reference (installed vs latest, publisher, downloads, update flag), and plugin runtime activity (request rate + datasource latency).",
  "tags": ["grafana-12", "v12.1", "advisor", "plugin-health", "v12-demo"],
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "version": 9,
  "editable": true,
  "refresh": "1m",
  "time": {"from": "now-1h", "to": "now"},
  "timepicker": {},
  "templating": {"list": [
    {
      "name": "ds_prom",
      "label": "Prometheus",
      "type": "datasource",
      "query": "prometheus",
      "current": {"selected": false, "text": "Prometheus", "value": "prom"},
      "refresh": 1,
      "hide": 0
    },
    {
      "name": "ds_grafana_api",
      "label": "Grafana API (Infinity)",
      "description": "Infinity DS pointing at this Grafana's own /api/plugins. Configure with allowedHosts including the Grafana base URL.",
      "type": "datasource",
      "query": "yesoreyeram-infinity-datasource",
      "regex": "/^(?!.*[Mm]arketplace)(?!.*grafana\\.com).*$/",
      "current": {"selected": false, "text": "Grafana API (Infinity)", "value": "grafana-api"},
      "refresh": 1,
      "hide": 0
    },
    {
      "name": "ds_grafana_com",
      "label": "grafana.com Marketplace (Infinity)",
      "description": "Infinity DS pointing at https://grafana.com/api/plugins (no auth). Configure with allowedHosts including https://grafana.com.",
      "type": "datasource",
      "query": "yesoreyeram-infinity-datasource",
      "regex": "/(?:[Mm]arketplace|grafana\\.com)/",
      "current": {"selected": false, "text": "Grafana.com Marketplace", "value": "grafana-com"},
      "refresh": 1,
      "hide": 0
    }
  ]},
  "panels": [

    {
      "id": 1, "type": "text", "title": "",
      "gridPos": {"h": 4, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0},
      "options": {"mode": "markdown", "content": "### Grafana Advisor (12.1) — Plugin Health & Inventory\n\nThe **[➡ Advisor app](/a/grafana-advisor-app)** runs a fresh health pass and reports plugin / DS / SSO / dashboard issues. This dashboard surfaces the underlying signals: **inventory totals**, **signature & Angular distribution**, a **full plugin table** with marketplace cross-reference, and **runtime activity** from Prometheus.\n\n- 🟢 **Updated** — installed version matches grafana.com latest &nbsp; · &nbsp; 🔴 **Not Updated** — newer version available &nbsp; · &nbsp; 🟠 **Not Available** — bundled with Grafana / private build (not on marketplace)\n- **Has Update** uses Grafana's own background update check (`hasUpdate`) — independent of the marketplace JOIN."}
    },

    {
      "id": 10, "type": "stat", "title": "Total plugins",
      "gridPos": {"h": 5, "w": 4, "x": 0, "y": 4},
      "datasource": {"uid": "${ds_grafana_api}", "type": "yesoreyeram-infinity-datasource"},
      "targets": [{
        "refId": "A", "type": "json", "source": "url",
        "url": "/api/plugins?embedded=0", "url_options": {"method": "GET"},
        "parser": "backend", "format": "table",
        "columns": [{"selector": "id", "text": "plugin_id", "type": "string"}]
      }],
      "transformations": [{"id": "reduce", "options": {"reducers": ["count"], "mode": "reduceFields"}}],
      "options": {"reduceOptions": {"calcs": ["lastNotNull"]}, "colorMode": "value", "graphMode": "none"},
      "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {"unit": "short", "noValue": "0", "color": {"mode": "fixed", "fixedColor": "blue"}}, "overrides": []}
    },
    {
      "id": 11, "type": "stat", "title": "Data sources",
      "gridPos": {"h": 5, "w": 4, "x": 4, "y": 4},
      "datasource": {"uid": "${ds_grafana_api}", "type": "yesoreyeram-infinity-datasource"},
      "targets": [{
        "refId": "A", "type": "json", "source": "url",
        "url": "/api/plugins?embedded=0&type=datasource", "url_options": {"method": "GET"},
        "parser": "backend", "format": "table",
        "columns": [{"selector": "id", "text": "plugin_id", "type": "string"}]
      }],
      "transformations": [{"id": "reduce", "options": {"reducers": ["count"], "mode": "reduceFields"}}],
      "options": {"reduceOptions": {"calcs": ["lastNotNull"]}, "colorMode": "value", "graphMode": "none"},
      "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {"unit": "short", "noValue": "0", "color": {"mode": "fixed", "fixedColor": "purple"}}, "overrides": []}
    },
    {
      "id": 12, "type": "stat", "title": "Panels",
      "gridPos": {"h": 5, "w": 4, "x": 8, "y": 4},
      "datasource": {"uid": "${ds_grafana_api}", "type": "yesoreyeram-infinity-datasource"},
      "targets": [{
        "refId": "A", "type": "json", "source": "url",
        "url": "/api/plugins?embedded=0&type=panel", "url_options": {"method": "GET"},
        "parser": "backend", "format": "table",
        "columns": [{"selector": "id", "text": "plugin_id", "type": "string"}]
      }],
      "transformations": [{"id": "reduce", "options": {"reducers": ["count"], "mode": "reduceFields"}}],
      "options": {"reduceOptions": {"calcs": ["lastNotNull"]}, "colorMode": "value", "graphMode": "none"},
      "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {"unit": "short", "noValue": "0", "color": {"mode": "fixed", "fixedColor": "orange"}}, "overrides": []}
    },
    {
      "id": 13, "type": "stat", "title": "Apps",
      "gridPos": {"h": 5, "w": 4, "x": 12, "y": 4},
      "datasource": {"uid": "${ds_grafana_api}", "type": "yesoreyeram-infinity-datasource"},
      "targets": [{
        "refId": "A", "type": "json", "source": "url",
        "url": "/api/plugins?embedded=0&type=app", "url_options": {"method": "GET"},
        "parser": "backend", "format": "table",
        "columns": [{"selector": "id", "text": "plugin_id", "type": "string"}]
      }],
      "transformations": [{"id": "reduce", "options": {"reducers": ["count"], "mode": "reduceFields"}}],
      "options": {"reduceOptions": {"calcs": ["lastNotNull"]}, "colorMode": "value", "graphMode": "none"},
      "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {"unit": "short", "noValue": "0", "color": {"mode": "fixed", "fixedColor": "green"}}, "overrides": []}
    },
    {
      "id": 14, "type": "stat", "title": "Signed (valid)",
      "description": "Plugins where signature=valid (cryptographically signed external plugins). Internal/unsigned excluded.",
      "gridPos": {"h": 5, "w": 4, "x": 16, "y": 4},
      "datasource": {"uid": "${ds_grafana_api}", "type": "yesoreyeram-infinity-datasource"},
      "targets": [{
        "refId": "A", "type": "json", "source": "url",
        "url": "/api/plugins?embedded=0", "url_options": {"method": "GET"},
        "parser": "backend", "format": "table",
        "columns": [
          {"selector": "id",        "text": "plugin_id", "type": "string"},
          {"selector": "signature", "text": "signature", "type": "string"}
        ]
      }],
      "transformations": [
        {"id": "filterByValue", "options": {"filters": [
          {"fieldName": "signature", "config": {"id": "regex", "options": {"value": "^valid$"}}}
        ], "type": "include", "match": "any"}},
        {"id": "reduce", "options": {"reducers": ["count"], "mode": "reduceFields"}}
      ],
      "options": {"reduceOptions": {"calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "/^plugin_id.*$/"}, "colorMode": "value", "graphMode": "none"},
      "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {"unit": "short", "noValue": "0", "color": {"mode": "fixed", "fixedColor": "green"}}, "overrides": []}
    },
    {
      "id": 15, "type": "stat", "title": "Angular detected",
      "description": "Plugins flagged angularDetected=true. Critical for v12 migration — Angular support removed in 12.0.",
      "gridPos": {"h": 5, "w": 4, "x": 20, "y": 4},
      "datasource": {"uid": "${ds_grafana_api}", "type": "yesoreyeram-infinity-datasource"},
      "targets": [{
        "refId": "A", "type": "json", "source": "url",
        "url": "/api/plugins?embedded=0", "url_options": {"method": "GET"},
        "parser": "backend", "format": "table",
        "columns": [
          {"selector": "id",              "text": "plugin_id", "type": "string"},
          {"selector": "angularDetected", "text": "angular",   "type": "string"}
        ]
      }],
      "transformations": [
        {"id": "filterByValue", "options": {"filters": [
          {"fieldName": "angular", "config": {"id": "regex", "options": {"value": "^true$"}}}
        ], "type": "include", "match": "any"}},
        {"id": "reduce", "options": {"reducers": ["count"], "mode": "reduceFields"}}
      ],
      "options": {"reduceOptions": {"calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "/^plugin_id.*$/"}, "colorMode": "background", "graphMode": "none"},
      "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {"unit": "short", "noValue": "0", "thresholds": {"mode": "absolute", "steps": [{"color": "green", "value": null}, {"color": "red", "value": 1}]}, "color": {"mode": "thresholds"}}, "overrides": []}
    },

    {
      "id": 20, "type": "stat", "title": "Updates available",
      "description": "Plugins where Grafana's background update check (hasUpdate) is true.",
      "gridPos": {"h": 5, "w": 6, "x": 0, "y": 9},
      "datasource": {"uid": "${ds_grafana_api}", "type": "yesoreyeram-infinity-datasource"},
      "targets": [{
        "refId": "A", "type": "json", "source": "url",
        "url": "/api/plugins?embedded=0", "url_options": {"method": "GET"},
        "parser": "backend", "format": "table",
        "columns": [
          {"selector": "id",        "text": "plugin_id",  "type": "string"},
          {"selector": "hasUpdate", "text": "has_update", "type": "string"}
        ]
      }],
      "transformations": [
        {"id": "filterByValue", "options": {"filters": [
          {"fieldName": "has_update", "config": {"id": "regex", "options": {"value": "^true$"}}}
        ], "type": "include", "match": "any"}},
        {"id": "reduce", "options": {"reducers": ["count"], "mode": "reduceFields"}}
      ],
      "options": {"reduceOptions": {"calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "/^plugin_id.*$/"}, "colorMode": "background", "graphMode": "none"},
      "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {"unit": "short", "noValue": "0", "thresholds": {"mode": "absolute", "steps": [{"color": "green", "value": null}, {"color": "orange", "value": 1}]}, "color": {"mode": "thresholds"}}, "overrides": []}
    },
    {
      "id": 21, "type": "stat", "title": "Plugin load errors (Advisor: BLOCKER)",
      "gridPos": {"h": 5, "w": 6, "x": 6, "y": 9},
      "datasource": {"uid": "${ds_prom}", "type": "prometheus"},
      "targets": [{"refId": "A", "datasource": {"uid": "${ds_prom}", "type": "prometheus"}, "expr": "sum(grafana_plugin_load_errors) or on() vector(0)"}],
      "options": {"reduceOptions": {"calcs": ["lastNotNull"]}, "colorMode": "background", "graphMode": "none"},
      "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {"noValue": "0", "thresholds": {"mode": "absolute", "steps": [{"color": "green", "value": null}, {"color": "red", "value": 1}]}, "color": {"mode": "thresholds"}}, "overrides": []}
    },
    {
      "id": 22, "type": "stat", "title": "Bundled with Grafana",
      "description": "Plugins where signature=internal (built-in panels and datasources).",
      "gridPos": {"h": 5, "w": 6, "x": 12, "y": 9},
      "datasource": {"uid": "${ds_grafana_api}", "type": "yesoreyeram-infinity-datasource"},
      "targets": [{
        "refId": "A", "type": "json", "source": "url",
        "url": "/api/plugins?embedded=0", "url_options": {"method": "GET"},
        "parser": "backend", "format": "table",
        "columns": [
          {"selector": "id",        "text": "plugin_id", "type": "string"},
          {"selector": "signature", "text": "signature", "type": "string"}
        ]
      }],
      "transformations": [
        {"id": "filterByValue", "options": {"filters": [
          {"fieldName": "signature", "config": {"id": "regex", "options": {"value": "^internal$"}}}
        ], "type": "include", "match": "any"}},
        {"id": "reduce", "options": {"reducers": ["count"], "mode": "reduceFields"}}
      ],
      "options": {"reduceOptions": {"calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "/^plugin_id.*$/"}, "colorMode": "value", "graphMode": "none"},
      "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {"unit": "short", "noValue": "0", "color": {"mode": "fixed", "fixedColor": "blue"}}, "overrides": []}
    },
    {
      "id": 23, "type": "stat", "title": "External plugins",
      "description": "Plugins NOT signed as 'internal' (third-party / Grafana Labs add-ons / community).",
      "gridPos": {"h": 5, "w": 6, "x": 18, "y": 9},
      "datasource": {"uid": "${ds_grafana_api}", "type": "yesoreyeram-infinity-datasource"},
      "targets": [{
        "refId": "A", "type": "json", "source": "url",
        "url": "/api/plugins?embedded=0", "url_options": {"method": "GET"},
        "parser": "backend", "format": "table",
        "columns": [
          {"selector": "id",        "text": "plugin_id", "type": "string"},
          {"selector": "signature", "text": "signature", "type": "string"}
        ]
      }],
      "transformations": [
        {"id": "filterByValue", "options": {"filters": [
          {"fieldName": "signature", "config": {"id": "regex", "options": {"value": "^internal$"}}}
        ], "type": "exclude", "match": "any"}},
        {"id": "reduce", "options": {"reducers": ["count"], "mode": "reduceFields"}}
      ],
      "options": {"reduceOptions": {"calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "/^plugin_id.*$/"}, "colorMode": "value", "graphMode": "none"},
      "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {"unit": "short", "noValue": "0", "color": {"mode": "fixed", "fixedColor": "purple"}}, "overrides": []}
    },

    {
      "id": 30, "type": "bargauge", "title": "Plugins by Type",
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 8, "x": 0, "y": 14},
      "datasource": {"uid": "${ds_grafana_api}", "type": "yesoreyeram-infinity-datasource"},
      "targets": [{
        "refId": "A", "type": "json", "source": "url",
        "url": "/api/plugins?embedded=0", "url_options": {"method": "GET"},
        "parser": "backend", "format": "table",
        "columns": [
          {"selector": "id",   "text": "plugin_id", "type": "string"},
          {"selector": "type", "text": "type",      "type": "string"}
        ]
      }],
      "transformations": [
        {"id": "groupBy", "options": {"fields": {
          "type":      {"aggregations": [], "operation": "groupby"},
          "plugin_id": {"aggregations": ["count"], "operation": "aggregate"}
        }}}
      ],
      "options": {"orientation": "horizontal", "displayMode": "gradient", "showUnfilled": true, "valueMode": "color", "reduceOptions": {"calcs": ["lastNotNull"]}},
      "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {"unit": "short", "noValue": "0", "color": {"mode": "palette-classic"}}, "overrides": []}
    },
    {
      "id": 31, "type": "bargauge", "title": "Plugins by Signature",
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 8, "x": 8, "y": 14},
      "datasource": {"uid": "${ds_grafana_api}", "type": "yesoreyeram-infinity-datasource"},
      "targets": [{
        "refId": "A", "type": "json", "source": "url",
        "url": "/api/plugins?embedded=0", "url_options": {"method": "GET"},
        "parser": "backend", "format": "table",
        "columns": [
          {"selector": "id",        "text": "plugin_id", "type": "string"},
          {"selector": "signature", "text": "signature", "type": "string"}
        ]
      }],
      "transformations": [
        {"id": "groupBy", "options": {"fields": {
          "signature": {"aggregations": [], "operation": "groupby"},
          "plugin_id": {"aggregations": ["count"], "operation": "aggregate"}
        }}}
      ],
      "options": {"orientation": "horizontal", "displayMode": "gradient", "showUnfilled": true, "valueMode": "color"},
      "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {"unit": "short", "noValue": "0", "color": {"mode": "palette-classic"}}, "overrides": []}
    },
    {
      "id": 32, "type": "piechart", "title": "Update availability (hasUpdate)",
      "description": "Distribution of Grafana's own hasUpdate flag across all installed plugins.",
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 8, "x": 16, "y": 14},
      "datasource": {"uid": "${ds_grafana_api}", "type": "yesoreyeram-infinity-datasource"},
      "targets": [{
        "refId": "A", "type": "json", "source": "url",
        "url": "/api/plugins?embedded=0", "url_options": {"method": "GET"},
        "parser": "backend", "format": "table",
        "columns": [
          {"selector": "id",        "text": "plugin_id",  "type": "string"},
          {"selector": "hasUpdate", "text": "has_update", "type": "string"}
        ]
      }],
      "transformations": [
        {"id": "groupBy", "options": {"fields": {
          "has_update": {"aggregations": [], "operation": "groupby"},
          "plugin_id":  {"aggregations": ["count"], "operation": "aggregate"}
        }}}
      ],
      "options": {"pieType": "donut", "displayLabels": ["name", "percent"], "legend": {"displayMode": "table", "placement": "right", "values": ["value", "percent"]}, "reduceOptions": {"calcs": ["lastNotNull"]}},
      "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {"unit": "short", "noValue": "0", "color": {"mode": "palette-classic"}, "mappings": [
        {"type": "value", "options": {"true":  {"text": "Update available", "color": "orange"}}},
        {"type": "value", "options": {"false": {"text": "Up to date / bundled", "color": "green"}}}
      ]}, "overrides": []}
    },

    {
      "id": 2, "type": "table",
      "title": "Plugin Health (feeds Advisor) — full inventory",
      "description": "Joins local /api/plugins against grafana.com /api/plugins by plugin_id. Update Status is computed by transformation (binary equality between Installed Version and Latest Version Available). Has Update is Grafana's own background-check flag. Publisher / Downloads come from grafana.com marketplace metadata.",
      "gridPos": {"h": 24, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 22},
      "datasource": {"uid": "-- Mixed --", "type": "datasource"},
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "LOCAL",
          "datasource": {"uid": "${ds_grafana_api}", "type": "yesoreyeram-infinity-datasource"},
          "type": "json", "source": "url",
          "url": "/api/plugins?embedded=0", "url_options": {"method": "GET"},
          "parser": "backend", "root_selector": "", "format": "table",
          "columns": [
            {"selector": "id",                            "text": "plugin_id",         "type": "string"},
            {"selector": "name",                          "text": "name",              "type": "string"},
            {"selector": "info.author.name",              "text": "author",            "type": "string"},
            {"selector": "type",                          "text": "plugin_type",       "type": "string"},
            {"selector": "info.version",                  "text": "installed_version", "type": "string"},
            {"selector": "hasUpdate",                     "text": "has_update",        "type": "string"},
            {"selector": "info.updated",                  "text": "last_updated",      "type": "string"},
            {"selector": "dependencies.grafanaDependency","text": "grafana_dep_local", "type": "string"},
            {"selector": "signature",                     "text": "signature",         "type": "string"},
            {"selector": "angularDetected",               "text": "angular",           "type": "string"}
          ]
        },
        {
          "refId": "MARKETPLACE",
          "datasource": {"uid": "${ds_grafana_com}", "type": "yesoreyeram-infinity-datasource"},
          "type": "json", "source": "url",
          "url": "https://grafana.com/api/plugins?orderBy=name&direction=asc",
          "url_options": {"method": "GET"},
          "parser": "backend", "root_selector": "items", "format": "table",
          "columns": [
            {"selector": "slug",      "text": "plugin_id",      "type": "string"},
            {"selector": "version",   "text": "latest_version", "type": "string"},
            {"selector": "orgName",   "text": "publisher",      "type": "string"},
            {"selector": "downloads", "text": "downloads",      "type": "number"}
          ]
        }
      ],
      "transformations": [
        {"id": "joinByField", "options": {"byField": "plugin_id", "mode": "outer"}},
        {"id": "calculateField", "options": {
          "mode": "binary",
          "binary": {"left": "installed_version", "operator": "==", "right": "latest_version"},
          "alias": "match", "replaceFields": false
        }},
        {"id": "organize", "options": {
          "renameByName": {
            "plugin_id":         "Plugin",
            "name":              "Name",
            "author":            "Author",
            "plugin_type":       "Type",
            "installed_version": "Installed Version",
            "latest_version":    "Latest Version Available",
            "match":             "Update Status",
            "has_update":        "Has Update",
            "publisher":         "Publisher",
            "downloads":         "Downloads",
            "last_updated":      "Last Updated",
            "grafana_dep_local": "Grafana Dependency",
            "signature":         "Signature",
            "angular":           "Angular"
          },
          "indexByName": {
            "plugin_id": 0, "name": 1, "author": 2, "plugin_type": 3,
            "installed_version": 4, "latest_version": 5, "match": 6,
            "has_update": 7, "publisher": 8, "downloads": 9,
            "last_updated": 10, "grafana_dep_local": 11,
            "signature": 12, "angular": 13
          }
        }}
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {"custom": {"cellOptions": {"type": "auto"}, "filterable": true, "align": "auto"}},
        "overrides": [
          {"matcher": {"id": "byName", "options": "Update Status"}, "properties": [
            {"id": "custom.cellOptions", "value": {"type": "color-background"}},
            {"id": "mappings", "value": [
              {"type": "value",   "options": {"1": {"color": "green",  "index": 0, "text": "Updated"}}},
              {"type": "value",   "options": {"0": {"color": "red",    "index": 1, "text": "Not Updated"}}},
              {"type": "special", "options": {"match": "null+nan", "result": {"color": "orange", "index": 2, "text": "Not Available"}}}
            ]},
            {"id": "custom.width", "value": 130},
            {"id": "noValue", "value": "Not Available"}
          ]},
          {"matcher": {"id": "byName", "options": "Has Update"}, "properties": [
            {"id": "custom.cellOptions", "value": {"type": "color-background"}},
            {"id": "mappings", "value": [
              {"type": "value", "options": {
                "true":  {"text": "YES", "color": "orange"},
                "false": {"text": "—",   "color": "green"}
              }}
            ]},
            {"id": "custom.width", "value": 100}
          ]},
          {"matcher": {"id": "byName", "options": "Plugin"},                  "properties": [{"id": "custom.width", "value": 240}]},
          {"matcher": {"id": "byName", "options": "Name"},                    "properties": [{"id": "custom.width", "value": 180}]},
          {"matcher": {"id": "byName", "options": "Author"},                  "properties": [{"id": "custom.width", "value": 150}]},
          {"matcher": {"id": "byName", "options": "Type"},                    "properties": [{"id": "custom.width", "value": 90}]},
          {"matcher": {"id": "byName", "options": "Installed Version"}, "properties": [
            {"id": "custom.width", "value": 150},
            {"id": "mappings", "value": [
              {"type": "special", "options": {"match": "empty",    "result": {"text": "Bundled (12.4.3)"}}},
              {"type": "special", "options": {"match": "null+nan", "result": {"text": "Bundled (12.4.3)"}}}
            ]},
            {"id": "noValue", "value": "Bundled (12.4.3)"}
          ]},
          {"matcher": {"id": "byName", "options": "Latest Version Available"}, "properties": [
            {"id": "custom.width", "value": 180},
            {"id": "mappings", "value": [
              {"type": "special", "options": {"match": "empty",    "result": {"text": "Bundled with Grafana"}}},
              {"type": "special", "options": {"match": "null+nan", "result": {"text": "Bundled with Grafana"}}}
            ]},
            {"id": "noValue", "value": "Bundled with Grafana"}
          ]},
          {"matcher": {"id": "byName", "options": "Publisher"}, "properties": [
            {"id": "custom.width", "value": 150},
            {"id": "noValue", "value": "—"}
          ]},
